name: Puzzles
description:
Over the course of my career, many
of my artworks have been censored
or deleted from my social media
portfolios for explicit content
violations. Ive seen the phrase "your
image has violated community
guidelines" too many times to count.
Both Instagram and Facebook have
flagged my account, making it almost
impossible to release new artworks to
their platforms. "Puzzles" is my third
release from the "Banned From The
Internet" series , I hope you enjoy :)
